cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and text compression. The use of recurrent neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper's focus on modeling long-term contextual information makes it relevant to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the use of syntactic parsing could also place it in the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category.
